    "Naturally, the method is not limited to car body shapes, but in itself, due to its complexity, the body of the car deserves higher attention, since it has to be designed to be aerodynamically competent, safe, and pleasant to the eye.",
    "The VAE is used to specify local features in the latent space, not just global ones.",
    "By combining optimization and MLP, the operator instructs the model to generate a specific car type that is different but real-like.",
